text: Aly Knepper (born 11 March 1940) is a Luxembourgian former sports shooter. He competed in the trap event at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:Living people Category:Luxembourgian male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Luxembourg Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Echternach
